  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   0.659656670690213         17.9502           413.94          1731.93
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.417106422095073        -11.3500          -261.74         -1095.11
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.151430749532538         -4.1206           -95.02          -397.58
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.044552745806776          1.2123            27.96           116.97
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.024462297950881         -0.6657           -15.35           -64.23
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.111209946918497          3.0262            69.79           291.98
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

